        Id Grade Path(s)                                                                                                                                                                     Details Requirements
bdl-pcsp-1 error  Bundle An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first. : entry.tail().where(resource is Composition).empty()          NaN

                                     Name                         Flags                         Card.                                                                                          Type                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Description & Constraints
                                   Bundle                             C                          0..*                                                                                        Bundle Survivorship Passport (SurPass) Bundle bdl-1: total only when a search or history bdl-2: entry.search only when a search bdl-3: entry.request mandatory for batch/transaction/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-4: entry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-7: FullUrl must be unique in a bundle, or else entries with the same fullUrl must have different meta.versionId (except in history bundles) bdl-9: A document must have an identifier with a system and a value bdl-10: A document must have a date bdl-11: A document must have a Composition as the first resource bdl-12: A message must have a MessageHeader as the first resource bdl-pcsp-1: An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first.
                            implicitRules                           ?!Σ                          0..1                                                                                           uri                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            A set of rules under which this content was created
                               identifier                             Σ                          1..1                                                                                    Identifier                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           Persistent identifier for the bundle
                                     type                             Σ                          1..1                                                                                          code                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   document | message | transaction | transaction-response | batch | batch-response | history | searchset | collection Binding: BundleType (required): Indicates the purpose of a bundle - how it is intended to be used. Fixed Value: document
                                timestamp                             Σ                          1..1                                                                                       instant                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  When the bundle was assembled
                         Slices for entry                            ΣC                          3..*                                                                               BackboneElement                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Entry resource in the SurPass bundle Slice: Unordered, Open by type:resource, profile:resource bdl-5: must be a resource unless there's a request or response bdl-8: fullUrl cannot be a version specific reference This repeating element order: For bundles of type 'document' and 'message', the first resource is special (must be Composition or MessageHeader respectively). For all bundles, the meaning of the order of entries depends on the bundle type

bdl-pcsp-1 error  Bundle An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first. : entry.tail().where(resource is Composition).empty()          NaN

Type                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Description & Constraints
                                   Bundle                             C                          0..*                                                                                        Bundle Survivorship Passport (SurPass) Bundle bdl-1: total only when a search or history bdl-2: entry.search only when a search bdl-3: entry.request mandatory for batch/transaction/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-4: entry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-7: FullUrl must be unique in a bundle, or else entries with the same fullUrl must have different meta.versionId (except in history bundles) bdl-9: A document must have an identifier with a system and a value bdl-10: A document must have a date bdl-11: A document must have a Composition as the first resource bdl-12: A message must have a MessageHeader as the first resource bdl-pcsp-1: An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first.

        Id Grade Path(s)                                                                                                                                                                     Details Requirements
bdl-pcsp-1 error  Bundle An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first. : entry.tail().where(resource is Composition).empty()          NaN

                                     Name                         Flags                         Card.                                                                                          Type                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Description & Constraints
                                   Bundle                             C                          0..*                                                                                        Bundle Survivorship Passport (SurPass) Bundle bdl-1: total only when a search or history bdl-2: entry.search only when a search bdl-3: entry.request mandatory for batch/transaction/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-4: entry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-7: FullUrl must be unique in a bundle, or else entries with the same fullUrl must have different meta.versionId (except in history bundles) bdl-9: A document must have an identifier with a system and a value bdl-10: A document must have a date bdl-11: A document must have a Composition as the first resource bdl-12: A message must have a MessageHeader as the first resource bdl-pcsp-1: An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first.

bdl-pcsp-1 error  Bundle An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first. : entry.tail().where(resource is Composition).empty()          NaN

                                     Name                         Flags                         Card.                                                                                          Type                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Description & Constraints
                                   Bundle                             C                          0..*                                                                                        Bundle Survivorship Passport (SurPass) Bundle bdl-1: total only when a search or history bdl-2: entry.search only when a search bdl-3: entry.request mandatory for batch/transaction/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-4: entry.response mandatory for batch-response/transaction-response/history, otherwise prohibited bdl-7: FullUrl must be unique in a bundle, or else entries with the same fullUrl must have different meta.versionId (except in history bundles) bdl-9: A document must have an identifier with a system and a value bdl-10: A document must have a date bdl-11: A document must have a Composition as the first resource bdl-12: A message must have a MessageHeader as the first resource bdl-pcsp-1: An SarPass document must have no additional Composition (including Composition subclass) resources besides the first.
